        <q>("(4) No order or regulations under section 4 may make provision such as is mentioned in subsection (I) which has the effect, in relation to any person who was a man of a reserve force immediately before the coming into force of the order or regulations concerned&#x2014;</p><p>
        <ol>
        <li>(a) of imposing a new or greater obligation on him without his consent, or</li>
        <li>(b) of varying or revoking, without his consent, a right to which he is entitled, not being a right exercisable only with the consent of another person or an authority.").</li>
