        Earl Howe moved Amendment No. 42:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0568P0-03151'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0568P0_19960123_GCR_136' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <q>Page 7, line 6, leave out ("(b)") and insert ("(a)").</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0568P0-03152'>
