      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0568P0-03198'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0568P0_19960123_GCR_183' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 21 [<span class="italic">Obligatory training of members of the reserve forces</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0568P0-03199'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0568P0_19960123_GCR_184' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Earl Howe</span> moved Amendment No. 54:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0568P0-03200'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0568P0_19960123_GCR_185' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <q>Page 9, line 14, leave out ("sections 22 and") and insert ("section").</q>
