            In directing your Lordships' attention to Clause 40, perhaps I may point out that Amendment
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_18gc' title='Col. 18GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 January 1996 vol 568 c18GC' name='column_18gc' href='#column_18gc' rel='bookmark'>18GC</a>
