        <span class="member">Earl Howe</span> moved Amendment No. 211:
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_32gc' title='Col. 32GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 January 1996 vol 568 c32GC' name='column_32gc' href='#column_32gc' rel='bookmark'>32GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0568P0-03682'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0568P0_19960123_GCR_667' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
