        <span class="member">Earl Howe</span> moved Amendment No. 213:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0568P0-03690'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0568P0_19960123_GCR_675' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
